|
*Released: 2007
*Label: Syco
*Format: DVD
|
*US: 2<U+00D7> Platinum<ref name=riaa/>
|
*Live concert performed on 27 June 2006 at the [[Greek Theatre (Los Angeles)|Greek Theater]] in Los Angeles, California as part of their World Tour 2006.
*Also features "The Time of our Lives" music video, performed with [[Toni Braxton]] as the official [[2006 FIFA World Cup]] song.
*Interviews with members of the group.
