==Music videos==
* "Unbreak My Heart (Regresa a mi)," filmed in [[Slovenia]], 2004 (directed by [[Sharon Maguire]]) [http://www.thecornerstore.tv/reels/sr_sharon_maguire/3.mov mov]
* "Mama," filmed in [[Italy]], 2005.
* "Time of our Lives," with Toni Braxton for the [[FIFA World Cup]], 2006 (directed by [[Nigel Dick]]).
* "The Power Of Love," filmed in [[Arena (colosseum)|Arena]] in [[Pula]], [[Croatia]], 2008.

